#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:2
msgid "PCB 拼板"
msgstr "PCB Array (Panel)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:4
msgid "本章介绍 PCB 拼板功能，包括管理子板模板、拼板列表管理、手动生成拼板、自动检测与自动调整、NG 子板标记等操作。"
msgstr ""
"This chapter covers the PCB Array (panel) feature — managing sub-board "
"templates, the panel list, manual array generation, auto-detect and auto-"
"adjust, and NG sub-board marking."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:7
msgid "界面结构"
msgstr "Layout"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:9
msgid "在产品编程页面顶部点击 **PCB 拼板** 标签页，进入拼板管理界面。"
msgstr ""
"On the product programming page, click the **PCB Array** tab at the top to "
"open the panel management view."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:-1
msgid "PCB 拼板界面"
msgstr "PCB Array view"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:15
msgid "界面左侧为功能标签页，包含三个标签："
msgstr "Three sub-tabs sit on the left:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:17
msgid "**管理子板模板** — 定义拼板基础单元的选择区域（Selection ROI），并支持自动检测子板位置。"
msgstr ""
"**Manage Base Panel** — define the **Selection ROI** that bounds a base sub-"
"board template, with optional auto-detect for sibling sub-board positions."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:18
msgid "**拼板列表** — 查看与管理已注册的各子板模板及其所有子板实例。"
msgstr ""
"**Panel List** — view and manage every registered base-panel template and "
"its sub-board instances."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:19
msgid "**手动生成拼板** — 通过标记点辅助手动指定子板排列（高级功能）。"
msgstr ""
"**Manual Panel Generation** — marker-pair-assisted manual sub-board layout "
"(advanced feature)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:22
msgid "管理子板模板"
msgstr "Manage Base Panel"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:24
msgid "**管理子板模板** 标签页用于定义子板的选择区域（Selection ROI）。选择区域决定哪些元件属于该子板，是拼板功能的基础。"
msgstr ""
"The **Manage Base Panel** sub-tab defines a sub-board's Selection ROI. The "
"Selection ROI decides which components belong to the sub-board and is the "
"foundation of the Array feature."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:26
msgid "**创建初始拼板单元**"
msgstr "**Create the initial base panel**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:28
msgid "**绘制矩形或多边形区域以创建拼板单元模板，选择所有相关元件，然后使用\"自动识别\"检测剩余拼板单元，使用\"自动调整拼板\"将元件框对齐。**"
msgstr ""
"**Draw a rectangle or polygon to create the base-panel template that selects"
" every related component, then use *Auto-Detect* to find the remaining sub-"
"boards and *Auto-Adjust Panel* to align the component boxes.**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:30
msgid ""
"点击 **矩形** 按钮，在右侧画布上框选第一个子板所在的区域；或点击 **多边形** "
"按钮，在场景上绘制多边形（左键添加顶点，右键删除上一个顶点，双击左键完成绘制）。"
msgstr ""
"Click **Rectangle** and box the area covering the first sub-board on the "
"right-hand canvas, or click **Polygon** and draw a polygon on the scene "
"(left-click adds a vertex, right-click removes the last vertex, double-click"
" finishes)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst
msgid "管理子板模板标签页：拼板单元矩形 / 多边形绘制工具与已定义子板列表"
msgstr ""
"Manage Base Panel sub-tab: rectangle / polygon drawing tools and the list of"
" defined sub-boards."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:36
msgid "绘制完成后，系统弹出对话框 **请输入子版模版标签**，输入该子板模板的名称（默认为 ``b0``），点击 **确认** 保存。"
msgstr ""
"After drawing, the **Enter Sub-Board Template Label** dialog opens. Type the"
" template name (default ``b0``) and click **Confirm** to save."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:38
msgid "新定义的子板模板出现在 **已定义的子板** 列表中，显示标签名称与 **实例** 数量。"
msgstr ""
"The newly-defined template appears in the **Defined Sub-Boards** list with "
"its label and **instance** count."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:40
msgid "**已定义的子板** 列表中，每个条目旁有 **手动生成拼板** 按钮，点击后切换至 **手动生成拼板** 标签页以进一步操作该子板模板。"
msgstr ""
"Each row in **Defined Sub-Boards** carries a **Manual Panel Generation** "
"button that switches to the **Manual Panel Generation** sub-tab for further "
"work on that template."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:42
msgid "**自动检测（自动识别子板位置）**"
msgstr "**Auto-Detect (find sub-board positions automatically)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:44
msgid "当至少存在一个已定义的子板模板后，页面下方显示 **自动检测** 按钮："
msgstr ""
"Once at least one base-panel template exists, the **Auto-Detect** button "
"appears at the bottom of the page:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:46
msgid "点击 **自动检测** 按钮，展开配置区域。"
msgstr "Click **Auto-Detect** to expand the configuration area."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:47
msgid "调整 **接受度** 滑块（0–100，默认 70），数值越高表示匹配精度要求越严格。"
msgstr ""
"Move the **Acceptance** slider (0–100, default 70); higher values demand "
"stricter matching."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:48
msgid "点击 **预览** 查看检测到的子板位置预览效果。"
msgstr "Click **Preview** to see the detected sub-board positions."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:49
msgid "预览满意后，点击 **保存** 完成自动检测并注册所有检测到的子板位置；点击 **取消** 放弃本次检测。"
msgstr ""
"When the preview looks right, click **Save** to register every detected "
"position; click **Cancel** to discard."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:52
msgid "拼板列表"
msgstr "Panel List"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:54
msgid "**拼板列表** 标签页展示所有已注册的子板模板及其下属子板实例，支持对各子板进行管理操作。标签页仅在至少存在一个已注册子板时可用。"
msgstr ""
"The **Panel List** sub-tab shows every registered base-panel template and "
"its sub-board instances, with management actions per row. The sub-tab is "
"enabled only when at least one sub-board exists."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:56
msgid "界面以树形结构显示：每个 **子板模板（BasePanelRow）** 下列出其所有子板实例。"
msgstr ""
"The list is a tree: each **Base Panel Row** carries its sub-board instances "
"underneath."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:58
msgid "**子板模板行操作**"
msgstr "**Actions on a base-panel row**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:60
msgid "每个子板模板行显示标签名称与实例数量，提供以下操作："
msgstr ""
"Each base-panel row shows the template label and the instance count and "
"exposes:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:62
msgid "**复制** — 在当前模板下新增一个子板实例（位置偏移约 15 像素）。"
msgstr ""
"**Duplicate** — add a sub-board instance under the same template (offset by "
"about 15 pixels)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:63
msgid "**手动生成拼板** — 切换至 **手动生成拼板** 标签页，对该模板进行手动子板布局。"
msgstr ""
"**Manual Panel Generation** — switch to the **Manual Panel Generation** sub-"
"tab for hand-tuned sub-board layout."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:64
msgid "**···（菜单）** — 展开下拉菜单，选择 **删除** 可移除该子板模板及其全部子板实例。"
msgstr ""
"**··· (menu)** — opens a drop-down; **Delete** removes the template and "
"every sub-board under it."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:66
msgid "**子板实例行操作**"
msgstr "**Actions on a sub-board instance row**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:68
msgid "每个子板实例行显示该子板的标签名称（如 ``b0-1``）。若子板已标记为 NG，标签以红色显示并附有 ``(NG)`` 后缀。操作包括："
msgstr ""
"Each row shows the sub-board's label (such as ``b0-1``). When the sub-board "
"is marked NG, the label turns red and is suffixed with ``(NG)``. Actions:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:70
msgid "**铅笔图标** — 点击可内联编辑该子板的标签名称，编辑完成后按 Enter 或点击 **保存** 提交。"
msgstr ""
"**Pencil icon** — click to edit the sub-board label inline; press Enter or "
"click **Save** to commit."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:71
msgid "**···（菜单）** — 展开下拉菜单，提供："
msgstr "**··· (menu)** — opens a drop-down with:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:73
msgid "**删除** — 移除该子板实例。"
msgstr "**Delete** — remove the sub-board instance."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:74
msgid "**标记为NG** / **取消NG标记** — 将该子板标记或取消标记为废板。标记后系统对该子板的所有元件设置 NG 状态。"
msgstr ""
"**Mark as NG / Clear NG mark** — mark or unmark the sub-board as wasted. "
"Marking it NG sets NG status on every component within."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst
msgid "删除拼板单元示意"
msgstr "Sub-board deletion illustration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst
msgid "拼板列表标签页：子板树形结构与 NG 标记入口"
msgstr "Panel List sub-tab: sub-board tree and the NG marking entry point"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:84
msgid "底部提供 **+ 添加子板模板** 按钮，点击后跳回 **管理子板模板** 标签页创建新的子板模板。"
msgstr ""
"The **+ Add Base Panel** button at the bottom jumps back to **Manage Base "
"Panel** to create another template."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:87
msgid "自动调整拼板"
msgstr "Auto-Adjust Panel"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:89
msgid "界面左侧底部的 **自动调整拼板** 按钮对已注册的所有子板执行图像对齐校正："
msgstr ""
"The **Auto-Adjust Panel** button at the bottom-left runs image-alignment "
"correction on every registered sub-board:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:91
msgid "系统对每个子板实例的元件框进行图像对齐，重新估算各子板的变换参数。"
msgstr ""
"The system image-aligns each sub-board's components and re-estimates the "
"per-sub-board transform."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:92
msgid "调整完成后，各子板的元件框会更新为校正后的位置（同步状态被设为独立，即后续对基础子板的编辑不再自动同步至已校正的子板）。"
msgstr ""
"After adjustment, each sub-board's component boxes are updated to the "
"corrected positions; sync state flips to independent, so later edits on the "
"base sub-board no longer auto-propagate to the corrected sub-boards."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:95
msgid "参数继承与同步原则"
msgstr "Parameter inheritance and sync rules"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:97
msgid "默认情况下，所有子板的检测参数（如 ROI、阈值、检测项）均继承基础子板的设置。"
msgstr ""
"By default, every sub-board inherits the base sub-board's inspection "
"parameters — ROIs, thresholds, inspection items."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:99
msgid "通过 **同步 ROI** 选项："
msgstr "Via the **Sync ROI** option:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst
msgid "同步 ROI 设置示意"
msgstr "Sync ROI option illustration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:105
msgid "（默认开启）开启时，对基础子板的调整会同步到同一模板下的所有子板实例。"
msgstr ""
"(On by default) When on, edits to the base sub-board propagate to every "
"sibling instance under the same template."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:106
msgid "关闭后，可对每个子板单独调整该元件的 ROI，适用于局部差异或特殊需求。"
msgstr ""
"When off, you can tune each sub-board's ROI independently — useful for local"
" variation or special cases."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:108
msgid "数据管理：数据集自动按元件分组，统计所有子板的检测结果。"
msgstr ""
"Data management: the dataset is automatically grouped by component and "
"aggregates results across every sub-board."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:111
msgid "条形码检测工具"
msgstr "Barcode tool"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:113
msgid "支持在拼板场景下识别每个子板的序列号、批次号等条码信息。"
msgstr ""
"In panel mode, each sub-board's serial number, batch number, and other "
"barcode data can be read independently."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:115
msgid "操作流程："
msgstr "Workflow:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:117
msgid "在模板编辑器中，先为基础子板添加条形码检测框，并分组为新元件。"
msgstr ""
"In the Template Editor, add a barcode ROI to the base sub-board and group it"
" as a new component."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:118
msgid "创建拼板后，系统会自动将该条形码检测框复制到所有子板。"
msgstr ""
"Once the panel is created, the barcode ROI is copied automatically to every "
"sub-board."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:119
msgid "检测时，系统可分别识别每个子板上的条码内容，并自动作为序列号归档。"
msgstr ""
"At inspection time, each sub-board's barcode is read separately and archived"
" as that sub-board's serial number."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:121
msgid "应用场景：追溯生产批次、定位异常子板、自动分组统计。"
msgstr ""
"Use cases: production-batch traceability, isolating an abnormal sub-board, "
"and automatic per-sub-board statistics."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:124
msgid "判废板阈值设置"
msgstr "Wasted-board threshold"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:126
msgid ""
"可在系统配置中为拼板设置整体判废板阈值。参考 :ref:`系统JSON配置`，编辑 "
"``wasted_array_board_failure_ratio`` 参数并保存。"
msgstr ""
"Configure the overall wasted-board threshold for arrays in the system "
"configuration. See :ref:`系统JSON配置`, edit "
"``wasted_array_board_failure_ratio``, and save."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:127
msgid "检测过程中，若任一子板的元件 NG 率超过该阈值，则该子板会被判定为废板并报出。"
msgstr ""
"During inspection, any sub-board whose component NG ratio exceeds this "
"threshold is judged wasted and reported."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:130
msgid "跳过此元件的检测"
msgstr "Skip inspection on this component"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:132
msgid ""
"**元件配置（ComponentInfo）** 面板提供 **跳过此元件的检测** "
"开关。开启后，该元件在检测时会被完全跳过：不参与推理、不出结果、也不计入 ``failure_ratio``\\ （包括子板判废逻辑）。"
msgstr ""
"The **Component Info** panel exposes a **Skip inspection on this component**"
" switch. When on, the component is skipped entirely at inspection time — no "
"inference, no result, not counted in ``failure_ratio`` (including the sub-"
"board verdict logic)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:134
msgid "适用场景：操作员临时排除已知有问题的元件，或排除当前没必要检测的元件。"
msgstr ""
"Use cases: temporarily excluding a component known to be problematic, or "
"excluding a component that doesn't need inspection right now."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:135
msgid "拼板行为：跳过设置会自动传播到 **同一元件在所有子板上的副本**。无需在每个子板上重复操作。"
msgstr ""
"Panel behavior: the skip setting propagates automatically to **every sub-"
"board copy of the same component**. No need to repeat it per sub-board."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:136
msgid "与坏板标记互斥：若元件已设置为 **坏板标记元件**，跳过开关会被锁定为关闭、不可修改。需要先取消坏板标记设置才能开启跳过。"
msgstr ""
"Mutually exclusive with badmark: if the component is configured as a "
"**badmark component**, the Skip switch is locked off. Clear the badmark "
"setting first."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:138
msgid "也可在模板编辑器中框选多个元件，使用右键菜单的 **跳过检测 / 清除跳过检测** 批量操作。"
msgstr ""
"You can also region-select multiple components in the Template Editor and "
"use the right-click menu's **Skip inspection / Clear skip inspection** for "
"batch operations."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:140
msgid "判定为跳过的元件在画布上会以 **半透明灰色虚线框** 显示，便于一眼区分。"
msgstr ""
"Skipped components are rendered on the canvas with a **translucent gray "
"dashed outline** so they're easy to spot."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:143
msgid "二维码序列号与拼板关联逻辑"
msgstr "QR-code serial-number assignment in panel mode"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:145
msgid ""
"序列号（MainSN / PanelSN）的生成与赋值规则取决于产品 **是否配置了拼板**，以及 **二维码识别框的位置**。下表覆盖 5 "
"种常见场景；请按实际配置对照排查 MES 报告中 MainSN / PanelSN 的取值是否符合预期。"
msgstr ""
"Serial number (MainSN / PanelSN) assignment depends on **whether the product"
" is panelized** and **where the QR-code ROI sits**. The table below covers 5"
" common scenarios — match your actual configuration against it to verify the"
" MainSN / PanelSN values in the MES report."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:147
msgid "二维码与拼板组合的序列号取值"
msgstr "Serial-number outcomes for QR-code × panel combinations"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:151
msgid "场景"
msgstr "Scenario"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:152
msgid "是否有拼板"
msgstr "Panelized?"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:153
msgid "二维码位置"
msgstr "QR-code location"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:154
msgid "整板序列号 (MainSN)"
msgstr "Main board SN (MainSN)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:155
msgid "拼板序列号 (PanelSN)"
msgstr "Sub-board SN (PanelSN)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:156
msgid "①"
msgstr "①"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:157
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:162
msgid "无拼板"
msgstr "No"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:158
msgid "无二维码"
msgstr "No QR code"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:159
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:170
msgid "自动生成"
msgstr "Auto-generated"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:160
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:165
msgid "—"
msgstr "—"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:161
msgid "②"
msgstr "②"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:163
msgid "≥1 个二维码框（取最后一个）"
msgstr "≥1 QR-code ROI (last one wins)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:164
