#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:184
msgid "**二维码读取常见问题：**"
msgstr "**Common QR-code issues:**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:186
msgid ""
"**二维码读取失败，序列号变成自动生成值**：检查二维码识别框是否完整覆盖条码区域；二维码本身是否清晰、无遮挡、无污损；多拼板时若部分拼板失败，检查拼板对齐是否偏移。"
msgstr ""
"**QR read fails and the serial number falls back to auto-generated**: check "
"that the QR ROI fully covers the barcode area; that the QR itself is sharp, "
"unobstructed, and unmarred; for panels, if only some sub-boards fail, check "
"whether the panel alignment has drifted."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:187
msgid ""
"**MES 报告中 MainSN / PanelSN 不符合预期**：对照上方场景表确认当前产品属于哪种场景。场景 ④ 中 MainSN "
"会自动取任意拼板的 PanelSN。如需 MainSN 为固定值，请在拼板区域外额外添加一个整板级二维码框，使产品落到场景 ⑤。"
msgstr ""
"**MES report's MainSN / PanelSN don't match expectations**: match the "
"product configuration against the scenario table above. In scenario ④, "
"MainSN is set to whichever panel's PanelSN happened to be picked. To pin "
"MainSN to a fixed value, add a board-level QR-code ROI outside the panel "
"area so the product falls into scenario ⑤."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:188
msgid "**阴阳板 / 鸳鸯板拼板**：智能拼板暂不支持此类布局，可使用 **手动复制粘贴拼板** 方式（旧拼板流程仍保留可用）。"
msgstr ""
"**Mixed-orientation / mirrored panels**: Smart PCB Array does not currently "
"support these layouts; use the legacy **manual copy-paste panel** flow "
"instead (still available)."

